Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.60,0:04:09.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乌丝科当配波卡\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK\fs14\b0\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H2F2F2F&\4c&H000000&}Uske taang pay ball kar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.65,0:04:13.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一说我就"懂"了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK\fs14\b0\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H2F2F2F&\4c&H000000&}Oh, that clears that up.
