Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.84,0:04:22.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去了巴基斯坦球星肖波连投俩脚前球的比赛\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK\fs14\b0\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H2F2F2F&\4c&H000000&}I was at the match when Shoaib bowled back-to-back yorkers.
