Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.55,0:04:32.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都有大概12万人左右\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK\fs14\b0\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H2F2F2F&\4c&H000000&}there's, like, 120,000 people.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.57,0:04:35.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得我们板球世界杯赢的几率如何\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK\fs14\b0\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H2F2F2F&\4c&H000000&}So what do you think of our chances at the World Cup?
