Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.10,0:04:39.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全看科利的打击手感好不好了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK\fs14\b0\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H2F2F2F&\4c&H000000&}You know, it'll all depend if Kohli's batting in form.
