Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.89,0:15:29.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉杰  我们都是科学家\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK\fs14\b0\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H2F2F2F&\4c&H000000&}Raj, we're scientists.
