Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.86,0:15:37.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这对恋爱的体验没有任何的影响\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK\fs14\b0\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H2F2F2F&\4c&H000000&}It doesn't take anything away from the experience.
